											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="(Cine) Next, in the centre of the sparks, you suddenly see a hand and lower arm coming out of the sigil. The hand opens and closes, looking for something to hold on to. A voice resounds, or so it seems, from deep within the stone." />
